                                <li data-v-7796d9ba="">Some knowledge of basic first aid could mean the difference between life and death.</li>
                                <li data-v-7796d9ba="" style="margin-top: 1rem;">Consider doing a first aid course, so that you will be able to manage if someone is injured or becomes ill.</li>
                                <li data-v-7796d9ba="" style="margin-top: 1rem;">CPR is a life-saving skill that everyone should learn.</li>
